data.description: Price Just Dropped! Just in time for you to be HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS! Welcome to East Tennessee, Country Living and Mountain Views Right Here. The only thing missing is you! 758 Grassy Hollow Rd offers a short drive to town on a paved road but country living at its very best. This beautiful home that is move in ready - Seller has provide a free copy of a home inspection report, a copy of the engineer report dated 2022 is on file, showing the home passed the requirements of HUD 's guide for a permanent foundation for manufactured housing. A metal roof and new decks with TREX materials for long lasting, weather resistant, low maintenance living has been installed. The ground is a blank slate ready for you to plant your favorite trees, shrubs, and flowers.  Of course, you're in the country so there is plenty of room for a garden!  Come experience all the sounds and sights of nature without driving miles out into the woods! This beautiful renovated three-bedroom, two-bathroom home nestled on just under an acre of land provides ample space for outdoor enjoyment and recreation. Enjoy breathtaking Tennessee mountain views that will leave you in awe. The interior of this home has been thoughtfully updated, offering modern comfort and style. The three bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, in this home is perfect for families or anyone seeking a peaceful retreat in the heart of nature. The stainless-steel appliances and washer/dryer combo will remain with the home. Home has luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, newly installed electric fireplace with a shiplap accent wall. Home is less than 10 minutes from the City of Harrogate or Tazewell. with just a very short drive to the Powell River, Norris Lake, or the Cumberland Gap National Park one can take advantage of all the wonderful outdoor adventures that Claiborne County and East Tennessee has to offer. Don't miss this opportunity to make this Mountain View Oasis your own!
